# Cloud Forge Run + Auto Runtime vocabulary (038)

**Law:** `brain-os/law/enforcement/SOURCEA_CLOUD_FORGE_RUN_AUTO_RUNTIME_VOCABULARY_LOCKED_v1.md`  
**SSOT:** `data/cloud-motor-founder-vocabulary-v1.json`

## One law

> **Say Cloud Forge Run (not drain). Say Auto Runtime (not loop). Anti-poison activated — internal `cloud-forge-run-*` paths stay for APIs.**

| Poison (forbidden founder chat) | Say instead |
|---------------------------------|-------------|
| drain · Cloud Forge Run · Cloud Forge Run | **Cloud Forge Run** |
| loop · Cloud Forge Run · drain loop | **Auto Runtime** |

## Agents MUST NOT

- Use “drain” or “loop” in founder-facing replies about the cloud motor
- Rename API paths in chat to confuse founder (`/api/cloud-forge-run/` → “Forge Run queue API” is OK)

